Let's save the rest
for tomorrow.

40
00:03:19.359 --> 00:03:20.623
- Aw.
- Bummer.

41
00:03:20.624 --> 00:03:22.933
You all get tucked into bed.
all right?

42
00:03:22.934 --> 00:03:24.593
Boo.

43
00:03:26.740 --> 00:03:29.840
I'll be right back.

44
00:03:32.339 --> 00:03:35.043
♪ ♪

45
00:03:46.254 --> 00:03:48.959
Princess Rosalina.

46
00:03:48.960 --> 00:03:51.731
you're coming with me.

47
00:03:51.732 --> 00:03:54.425
♪ ♪

48
00:04:27.229 --> 00:04:29.933
