49
00:04:43.949 --> 00:04:46.016
You messed with the wrong...

50
00:04:46.017 --> 00:04:47.952
Mama?

51
00:04:47.953 --> 00:04:50.547
I had a bad dream.

52
00:04:50.747 --> 00:04:54.188
Uh-oh. It wasn't a dream.

53
00:05:07.808 --> 00:05:10.072
Wha...?

54
00:05:33.757 --> 00:05:39.102
From the ashes of his father's
defeat rises a new conqueror.

55
00:05:39.103 --> 00:05:43.469
The Bowser name
shall be feared once more.

56
00:05:45.505 --> 00:05:46.945
Will you shut up?

57
00:05:46.946 --> 00:05:49.376
I'm just so happy for you.

58
00:05:49.377 --> 00:05:52.313
Your first princess-napping!

59
00:05:54.118 --> 00:05:56.118
Leave my mama alone!

60
00:05:56.483 --> 00:05:58.319
No!

61
00:06:10.563 --> 00:06:13.300
♪ ♪

62
00:06:17.603 --> 00:06:20.340
♪ ♪

63
00:06:41.627 --> 00:06:43.496
Huh?

64
00:06:50.471 --> 00:06:52.867
Wahoo!

65
00:06:55.806 --> 00:06:58.543
♪ ♪

66
00:07:15.969 --> 00:07:17.936
Woo-hoo!

67
00:07:22.041 --> 00:07:24.734
