68
00:07:25.341 --> 00:07:28.309
Woo-hoo!

69
00:07:44.624 --> 00:07:46.064
Hey. huh?

70
00:07:46.065 --> 00:07:48.759
Lu. that jump you hit
back there...

71
00:07:48.760 --> 00:07:51.927
Mario. are we cool
motorcycle guys now?

72
00:07:51.928 --> 00:07:52.730
Obviously.

73
00:07:52.731 --> 00:07:54.974
- Oh. you're here.
- Oh.

74
00:07:54.975 --> 00:07:57.570
Now. where's
the troubled pipes?

75
