01:12:22.597 --> 01:12:26.633
helps you remember
your true calling.

829
01:12:26.634 --> 01:12:29.405
My Koopas...

830
01:12:29.406 --> 01:12:31.539
your king has returned!

831
01:13:13.318 --> 01:13:15.450
♪ ♪

832
01:13:38.310 --> 01:13:40.806
We'll get you on the planet.

833
01:13:40.807 --> 01:13:42.247
Buckle up.

834
01:13:42.248 --> 01:13:45.282
It's about to get crazy.

835
01:13:46.483 --> 01:13:49.748
Star Fox team is ready.

836
01:13:51.224 --> 01:13:52.752
Sick.

837
01:14:14.544 --> 01:14:15.951
♪ ♪

838
01:14:19.450 --> 01:14:20.714
Let's do this.

839
01:14:26.457 --> 01:14:29.128
Incoming!

840
01:14:32.133 --> 01:14:34.662
Do a barrel roll!

841
01:14:36.368 --> 01:14:38.204
Yay!

842
01:14:48.413 --> 01:14:50.249
You're up. Mustache!

843
01:14:50.250 --> 01:14:52.415
Good luck.

844
01:14:56.223 --> 01:14:58.586
Wahoo!

845
01:15:15.506 --> 01:15:17.737
Wahoo!

846
01:15:35.460 --> 01:15:38.264
I don't know what that means.

847
01:15:38.265 --> 01:15:41.465
It means you go this way.
we go that way.

848
01:15:41.466 --> 01:15:43.136
Oh. Got ya.

849
01:15:44.271 --> 01:15:46.964
♪ ♪

850
01:16:02.817 --> 01:16:05.554
♪ ♪

851
01:16:25.147 --> 01:16:27.774
Oh.

852
01:16:33.683 --> 01:16:36.256
Intruder alert! Intruder alert!

853
01:16:36.257 --> 01:16:38.191
Get them!

854
01:16:41.295 --> 01:16:42.955
It won't be long now. Dad.

855
01:16:42.956 --> 01:16:45.232
What?!

856
01:16:45.233 --> 01:16:49.368
My lords.
our tormentors have returned!

857
01:16:50.667 --> 01:16:52.030
I'll take care of 'em.

858
01:16:52.031 --> 01:16:56.770
I built a security system
that's next-level.

859
01:16:59.313 --> 01:17:02.216
They're gonna get
torn to pieces.

860
01:17:03.713 --> 01:17:05.120
I love being a dad.

861
01:17:05.121 --> 01:17:10.256
Oh. the days are long.
but the years are short.

862
01:17:30.212 --> 01:17:33.840
Hello. Peach and Mario.

863
01:17:35.316 --> 01:17:39.077
Prepare to meet your maker.

864
01:17:48.791 --> 01:17:51.055
♪ ♪

865
01:18:09.284 --> 01:18:12.483
♪ ♪

866
01:18:38.577 --> 01:18:40.907
Whoa!

867
01:18:48.818 --> 01:18:51.984
I've got you now.

868
01:19:12.281 --> 01:19:14.282
♪ ♪

869
01:19:14.283 --> 01:19:16.107
Woo-hoo!

870
01:19:20.256 --> 01:19:23.455
("Course Clear" playing)

871
01:19:28.429 --> 01:19:32.464
I won't let them ruin this.

872
01:19:53.322 --> 01:19:54.553
Bowser.

873
01:19:56.083 --> 01:19:57.853
It didn't have to be this way.

874
01:19:57.854 --> 01:20:01.120
I know there's still
some good in there.

875
01:20:05.796 --> 01:20:08.160
♪ ♪

876
01:20:08.161 --> 01:20:10.536
Let us pass. Now.

877
01:20:10.537 --> 01:20:11.372
Or what?

878
01:20:11.373 --> 01:20:13.066
You'll humiliate me
at my wedding?

879
01:20:13.067 --> 01:20:16.971
Shrink me to a nubbin
and put me in a jar?

880
01:20:16.972 --> 01:20:19.039
Make me join a book club?!

881
01:20:19.040 --> 01:20:20.315
We had our moment. Mario.

882
01:20:20.316 --> 01:20:26.420
but Bowser is back.
and now you'll feel my fury!

883
01:20:34.121 --> 01:20:37.155
♪ ♪

884
01:20:47.442 --> 01:20:50.136
No. No. No...!

885
01:20:53.008 --> 01:20:54.613
Dad!

886
01:20:54.614 --> 01:20:57.351
♪ ♪

887
01:21:13.666 --> 01:21:16.194
Dad.

888
01:21:25.205 --> 01:21:27.876
♪ ♪

889
01:21:36.524 --> 01:21:38.921
I am the lord of bones!

890
01:21:38.922 --> 01:21:41.627
I am the skull king!

891
01:21:41.628 --> 01:21:43.992
And I'm his son!

892
01:21:59.745 --> 01:22:01.107
Mario!

893
01:22:02.517 --> 01:22:03.748
Go.

894
01:22:03.749 --> 01:22:05.485
Save her.

895
01:22:32.811 --> 01:22:34.372
Oh!

896
01:22:34.373 --> 01:22:35.945
Whoa! Oh!

897
01:22:52.600 --> 01:22:54.600
Whoa!

898
01:22:58.936 --> 01:23:01.431
♪ ♪

899
01:23:16.855 --> 01:23:18.624
Ow!

900
01:23:19.792 --> 01:23:21.957
Yoshi.

901
01:23:22.531 --> 01:23:25.862
("Power-Up" plays)

902
01:23:26.128 --> 01:23:27.425
Very weird.

903
01:23:36.402 --> 01:23:38.545
Ow!

904
01:23:42.276 --> 01:23:44.881
Whoa!

905
01:23:58.897 --> 01:24:00.997
Whoa!

906
01:24:00.998 --> 01:24:02.966
("Power-Down" plays)

907
01:24:07.169 --> 01:24:10.072
("Power-Down" plays)

908
01:24:30.797 --> 01:24:33.490
♪ ♪

909
01:24:33.965 --> 01:24:35.394
Finish this. Lu.

910
01:24:40.675 --> 01:24:41.774
Ha!

911
01:24:41.775 --> 01:24:43.039
- Lu!
- What?

912
01:24:43.040 --> 01:24:45.173
You know I never learned
how to draw!

913
01:24:57.285 --> 01:24:58.548
Yes!

914
01:24:59.254 --> 01:25:00.518
No!

915
01:25:34.696 --> 01:25:36.290
In the name of the Koopas...

916
01:25:40.900 --> 01:25:41.669
Junior!

917
01:25:41.670 --> 01:25:45.364
Daddy! Please help me!

918
01:25:49.370 --> 01:25:52.140
Junior!

919
01:25:54.111 --> 01:25:56.210
♪ ♪

920
01:25:56.608 --> 01:25:59.147
("Power-Up" plays)

921
01:26:15.297 --> 01:26:17.737
♪ ♪

922
01:26:23.910 --> 01:26:25.746
Dad!

923
01:26:25.747 --> 01:26:27.978
Oh. my boy.

924
01:26:58.505 --> 01:27:00.879
Rosalina.

925
01:27:07.052 --> 01:27:09.987
I need you to try.

926
01:27:15.621 --> 01:27:18.358
♪ ♪

927
01:27:23.464 --> 01:27:26.168
♪ ♪

928
01:27:58.697 --> 01:28:01.841
♪ ♪

929
01:28:02.074 --> 01:28:04.910
I knew you would come for me.

930
01:28:07.145 --> 01:28:10.609
Hey! Found your femur. Dad.

931
01:28:10.610 --> 01:28:11.885
Doing great. my boy.

932
01:28:11.886 --> 01:28:14.151
Let's find my foot.

933
01:28:14.152 --> 01:28:16.956
Mario! Mario.

934
01:28:16.957 --> 01:28:19.024
Come meet my sister.

935
01:28:19.025 --> 01:28:21.829
I am so happy
you found each other.

936
01:28:21.830 --> 01:28:24.128
I love a family reunion.

937
01:28:24.129 --> 01:28:25.899
Heyo!

938
01:28:38.011 --> 01:28:39.011
Mama?

939
01:28:39.012 --> 01:28:40.771
Oh. Mama.

940
01:28:40.772 --> 01:28:44.885
Oh. My babies.

941
01:28:44.886 --> 01:28:46.953
We missed you so much.

942
01:28:46.954 --> 01:28:48.152
I missed you. too.

943
01:28:48.153 --> 01:28:51.683
Mama. can we visit
the Mushroom Kingdom?

944
01:28:51.684 --> 01:28:53.289
I want to see the castle.

945
01:28:53.290 --> 01:28:55.291
Okay. okay.

946
01:29:02.728 --> 01:29:05.872
Where's your castle?

947
01:29:06.237 --> 01:29:07.633
Uh. well. the castle.

948
01:29:07.634 --> 01:29:09.668
Yeah. the castle. um...

949
01:29:09.669 --> 01:29:11.768
It died.

950
01:29:12.672 --> 01:29:15.080
What are you talking about?

951
01:29:15.081 --> 01:29:16.114
You know what. guys?

952
01:29:16.115 --> 01:29:19.282
We're gonna rebuild
the best castle ever.

953
01:29:19.283 --> 01:29:21.547
Who wants to help?

954
01:29:25.487 --> 01:29:28.356
- Oh. yeah.
- Woo-hoo!

955
01:29:28.655 --> 01:29:31.227
♪ ♪

956
01:29:37.004 --> 01:29:39.235
("Power-Down" plays)

957
01:29:52.085 --> 01:29:54.888
("Power-Up" plays)

958
01:29:59.389 --> 01:30:01.192
Wahoo!

959
01:30:01.193 --> 01:30:03.897
♪ ♪

960
01:30:11.236 --> 01:30:14.039
♪ ♪

961
01:30:39.099 --> 01:30:41.792
♪ ♪

962
01:31:11.131 --> 01:31:13.824
♪ ♪

963
01:31:38.455 --> 01:31:41.159
♪ ♪

964
01:32:10.784 --> 01:32:13.488
♪ ♪

965
01:32:31.244 --> 01:32:32.541
So. where are you off to next?

966
01:32:32.542 --> 01:32:35.709
That nice space princess
fixed up my warp drive.

967
01:32:35.710 --> 01:32:38.415
and I'm heading home.

968
01:32:38.416 --> 01:32:39.944
Good luck with them.

969
01:32:39.945 --> 01:32:43.320
That is one complicated family.

970
01:32:51.660 --> 01:32:53.298
Don't worry. son.

971
01:32:53.299 --> 01:32:55.102
No jail can hold us.

972
01:32:55.103 --> 01:32:56.895
We'll be out of here soon.

973
01:33:05.377 --> 01:33:07.004
Hello. maggots.

974
01:33:07.005 --> 01:33:08.808
Trying to escape?

975
01:33:09.876 --> 01:33:11.745
You're gonna play
by my rules now.

976
01:33:11.746 --> 01:33:13.351
Stay close. son.

977
01:33:13.352 --> 01:33:14.451
She won't break us.

978
01:33:14.452 --> 01:33:17.157
First goes the body.
then goes the bones.

979
01:33:17.158 --> 01:33:21.095
Then all that's left is dust.

980
01:33:21.096 --> 01:33:23.493
You be quiet right now.

981
01:33:23.494 --> 01:33:25.726
You can't silence the truth.

982
01:33:25.727 --> 01:33:27.167
It only makes it louder.

983
01:33:27.168 --> 01:33:30.995
Like the approaching
drumbeat of death!

984
01:33:32.701 --> 01:33:33.899
Boom. boom.

985
01:33:33.900 --> 01:33:37.968
- boom. boom.
- No!

986
01:33:39.576 --> 01:33:42.280
♪ ♪

987
01:34:11.608 --> 01:34:14.312
♪ ♪

988
01:34:43.343 --> 01:34:46.036
♪ ♪

989
01:35:15.375 --> 01:35:18.068
♪ ♪

990
01:35:47.407 --> 01:35:50.100
♪ ♪

991
01:36:19.439 --> 01:36:22.132
♪ ♪

992
01:36:51.471 --> 01:36:54.164
♪ ♪

993
01:37:23.503 --> 01:37:26.196
♪ ♪

994
01:37:45.921 --> 01:37:49.121
Oh. There. there.
you poor little monkey.

995
01:37:49.122 --> 01:37:51.189
Ow.

996
01:37:59.033 --> 01:38:01.573
Well. thank you very much...

997
01:38:01.574 --> 01:38:03.377
Your Highness.

998
01:38:03.378 --> 01:38:04.972
♪ ♪

